author: A_Brickset_user
title: Me brother got this in his stocking. Weeeeeeee!!!!!
review: This is good for tricking out a space port. There is 2 helmets, 2 visors, 2signs, some stickers, a signpole, and a lot o' space port logos. Yea! It is cool, highly reccomended. They still have a few left on LEGO.com.
